NOTICE — Unofficial Fan Localization (Not Affiliated with the Game)
=================================================================

This project is an **unofficial, non-commercial, volunteer fan localization**
for "The Guild - Europa 1410". Its sole purpose is to help players who
**already legally own the game** experience it in Russian.

**This is NOT:**

- Piracy, cracking, or DRM circumvention
- A game dump, repack, or substitute for purchasing the game
- Hacking, cheating, or modification of game executable code
- An official or endorsed product of the publisher or developer

**This IS:**

- A community translation overlay (text localization mod files)
- Free fan work with **no commercial claims**
- A mod that requires a legitimate game installation to function

**Intellectual property:**

All rights to "The Guild - Europa 1410", including but not limited to
trademarks, characters, story, audio, visuals, and original English text,
belong exclusively to the respective rights holders (including THQ Nordic
and associated parties).

Contributors to this project **claim no ownership** of any game intellectual
property. Only community-created Russian translations and build scripts are
shared here.

**Repository contents:** build tools and translation data. No game binaries.

**Release archives:** localization mod files only (`.pak`, `.ucas`, `.utoc`)
plus a disclaimer. The game itself is never distributed.

**User obligations:**

1. Own a legal copy of the game before using this mod.
2. Use for personal, non-commercial purposes only.
3. Do not redistribute game assets obtained from the installation.

**Takedown policy:**

Rights holders may contact us via GitHub Issues. We will review and comply
with valid requests promptly.

See [DISCLAIMER.md](DISCLAIMER.md) for the full statement in Russian and English.
